<item>
            <title>[OAK-3433] Background update may create journal entry with incorrect id</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/OAK-3433</link>
                <project id="12313221" key="OAK">Jackrabbit Oak</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The conflict check does not consider changes that are made visible between the rebase and the background read.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
